# Tauola steering options
Define TauolaCurrentOption 1
Define TauolaBR1 1.0
#
Alias         Mytau+     tau+
Alias         Mytau-     tau-
ChargeConj    Mytau+     Mytau-
#
Decay B+sig
  0.500       K+      Mytau+     mu-        PHSP;
  0.500       K+      mu+        Mytau-     PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay B-sig
#
Decay Mytau-
  1.00        TAUOLA 8;
Enddecay
CDecay Mytau+
#
End
